{"type": "article", "id": 30401, "title": "悬浮无线充电器", "description": "", "date": "2016-08-01T23:05:18Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 1, "praise_count": 46, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160801181321PKYMs6HGOme7uQlx.jpg", "contents": "<p>          </p><p>无线充电已经不再稀奇了，AR Designs 推出的 OvRcharge 选择在充电“姿势”上下功夫，为充电设备增加了悬浮功能。为了实现悬浮的效果，使用时需要安装配套的超薄手机壳或者 7 毫米厚的适配器，两者均内置了电力感应接收器和磁铁。这是它的<a href=\"https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/261307172/ovrcharge-levitating-wireless-charger\" rel=\"nofollow\">众筹链接</a>，最低价为 229 加元。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160801181406rTyCJjtqe1UhiXod.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.627941\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160801181406KweDB4glM3VO0cTG.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.560472\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/2016080118140680wTZCUKpPcb1nmx.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.563235\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160801181407jiRQJ3dGIxrE5DU7.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.588235\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>"}